<br>
I fought the buffed up Fennin Ro today and I think he is getting fairly close to what all PoP bosses should be in terms of endurance vs speed.  Verent went a little overboard with the extreme DPS output, Low Hitpoint mobs in PoP.  Many bosses really need their HP upped some while slightly lowering their DPS output.<br>
