If you cant answer that question because you have yet to go there, then how can you say its too easy to do everything in PoP? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jadrax>Jadrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1133<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/03 6:14 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ is dying</span><hr size=1> Grave yards save you the 15mins of logging on your alt necro. That is not making the game easier.<br>
<br>
The only thing that matters is how hard are all the bosses to kill, and how much time it will take to get to that point of hardness. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=carighanmaconar01>CarighanMaconar01</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/03 6:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ is dying</span><hr size=1> And even considering GYs only have 15 minutes - doesn't it make you feel a bit more comfortable if you know even with NO single Necro in the game, you can safely die in the last spot in a plane and still get your corpse back?<br>
<br>
It is right, EQis trivialized to an extend it is crap <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Basically, when i began EQ (shortly after launch), i had to ask others for everything (-&gt; social interaction). Hell, i went to BB, with 3 others, none of us knew what was there (-&gt; new content, exploration). Died? Oh, in Erudin again (-&gt; no bind wores). THAT was content which, thou often repelling, made you watch your step [u]very[/u] closely. Nowadays, dieing is np, summon, rezz, modrod, 2 twitches, rebuff, back to action... wheres the challenge behind that?<br>
<br>
Items never leave the game - thereby trivializing equipment in the long run. What do i speak, in the lonk run? Equipping a char IS trivialized...<br>
<br>
Everything is simply trivialized - Diablo II is a nice comparison, though i prefer Quake <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  And to say other games have it trivial from the beginning, well yeah, but there, the game is made about that. Not like EQ, which began as a hard game, and then became easier and easier... <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=55795">Carighan Maconar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Enchantress of the 59th Circle<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Member of the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.nebelwelt.de/eq/index.htm">Namenlose Bruderschaft</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> on Solusek Ro<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.mutedfaith.com/quiz/qz4.htm&quot;" target="&quot;new&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.mutedfaith.com/images/time.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.mutedfaith.com/quiz/qz4.htm&quot;" target="&quot;new&quot;">find your element</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> at <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.mutedfaith.com&quot;" target="&quot;new&quot;">mutedfaith.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=garrathmoore>Garrath Moore</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 570<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/03 7:33 am)<