<br>
And this is a bad thing because? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=myztic>MyztiC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Born-Again Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 688<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/03 8:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ is dying</span><hr size=1> Midget, I have ventured into PoP, I have seen Fennin Ro die and Xegony flap her wings at me. That's partly why I was posting, we're now 2 months into expansion and we're doing 2nd last zones with speed. The LoY won't help, as it is geared towards 1-60 level people.<br>
<br>
Elyia brought up a great point that I neglected to mention. In PoP you can win without excecution, just throw bodies at the mob. Good example would be RZ on some server where they had 180-200 people at that fight. That trivializes the content really fast. On fights like that it really don't matter how you excecute, as long as you do. Whereas with raid force of 50, it needs to be flawless and challenging. We all know people are lazy and want convenient, so unless VI fixes zerging, the guild with biggest number will come up on the top, not the guild with tactics. PoNB flag event for 18 people and the PoS event for 24 people are great because of the limit, one can't trivialize that kind of content too fast.<br>
<br>
And why is it bad that there are no more 12 hour CR's. I think it was one of the creators of EQ who said it 3+ years ago... something like &quot;If there are no drawbacks or punishment for failure, there isn't any challenge to overcome&quot;. That's why exp loss was huge deal back then, but today, who cares about few deaths... just rez and exp for 1 hour and you're in better shape than before.<br>
<br>
-myz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jadrax>Jadrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1138<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/03 8:17 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EQ is dying</span><hr size=1> BTW, summon corpse was added to EQ on dec 8th, 1999.<br>
